Package bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.data.sequence

This package contains the components used to model Biological Sequences.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BankSequenceInfo
    This interface defines a Sequence Information Object.
    BankSequenceInfoFactory
    This interface defines a Sequence Information Factory.
    DAlphabet
    This interface defines an alphabet.
    DAlphabetFactory
    This interface defines an alphabet factory.
    DFeatureSelectionModel
    This interface defines a Feature Selection model.
    DRulerModel
    This interface defines a ruler model.
    DSequence
    This interface implements a sequence
    DSequenceAligned
    This interface defines the wrapper of a DSequence aligned in a multiple sequence alignment.
    DSequenceAlignedFactory
    This interface defines a DSequenceAligned factory.
    DSequenceAlignment
    This interface defines a multiple sequence alignment.
    DSequenceAlignmentFactory
    This interface defines a DSequenceAlignment factory.
    DSequenceFactory
    This interface defines a sequence factory.
    DSymbol
    This interface defines a sequence symbol.
    DSymbolFactory
    This interface defines a symbol factory.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BankSequenceDescriptor
    This interface defines a sequence descriptor.
    DDefaultFeatureSelectionModel
    This class defines a Feature Selection model.
    DLocation
    This class represents a position on a sequence.
    DSequenceInfo
    This class is just used to set an identifier and a description to a DSequence.
    DSequenceModel
    This class implements a sequence model.
    DSeqUtils  
    DSymbolFamily
    This class defines a family of symbols.
    DSymbolFamilySystem
    This class manages families of symbols.
    DSymbolGraphics
    This class contains the graphical properties that can be associated to a symbol.
